Package: crmReporter
Type: Package
Title: Utility Functions for the Design and Reporting of CRM Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("John", "Kirkpatrick", email = "john.kirkpatrick@roche.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: John Kirkpatrick <john.kirkpatrick@roche.com>
Description: A collection of functions for summarising the results of both
   simulation studies during the design of a CRM trial, or for presenting the
   results of an actual CRM trial, either for dose escalation meetings or in
   the clinical study report.
